Span.Text: A custody reference is entered to which the evidence will be linked.
A list of evidence items associated with this custody reference is shown.
Before an evidence bag can be tagged, information relating to the item of evidence is added.
The device is tapped onto a NFC tag on the evidence bag which writes the evidence information to the tag and creates a record in the evidence store.
